# Activity Detail

## Summary

- Activity ID: {{ insight.activity.activity_id }}
- Date: {{ insight.activity.start_date.isoformat() }}
- Name: {{ insight.activity.name }}
- Sport: {{ insight.activity.sport_type }}
- Distance: {{ insight.activity.distance_kilometers }} km
- Moving time: {{ insight.activity.moving_time_minutes }} min
- Elapsed time: {{ insight.activity.elapsed_time_minutes }} min
- Elevation gain: {{ insight.activity.total_elevation_gain_meters or 0 }} m
- Average heart rate: {{ insight.activity.average_heartrate or "n/a" }}
- Max heart rate: {{ insight.activity.max_heartrate or "n/a" }}
- Average power: {{ insight.activity.average_watts or "n/a" }}
- Weighted average power: {{ insight.activity.weighted_average_watts or "n/a" }}
- Kilojoules: {{ insight.activity.kilojoules or "n/a" }}
- Load: {{ insight.load_score }} via {{ insight.load_source }}
- Tags: {{ insight.tags | join(", ") if insight.tags else "none" }}
{% if insight.interval_summary %}
- Interval note: {{ insight.interval_summary }}
{% endif %}

## Zones
{% if insight.activity.zones %}
{% for zone in insight.activity.zones %}
- {{ zone.resource }} zone {{ zone.zone_index }}: {{ zone.time_seconds }} seconds{% if zone.min_value is not none %}, min {{ zone.min_value }}{% endif %}{% if zone.max_value is not none %}, max {{ zone.max_value }}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- No zone data was available for this activity.
{% endif %}

## Laps
{% if insight.activity.laps %}
{% for lap in insight.activity.laps %}
- Lap {{ lap.lap_index }}{% if lap.name %} ({{ lap.name }}){% endif %}: {{ lap.distance_meters }} m, {{ lap.moving_time_seconds }} s, avg HR {{ lap.average_heartrate or "n/a" }}, avg W {{ lap.average_watts or "n/a" }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- No lap data was available for this activity.
{% endif %}

## Streams
{% if insight.activity.streams %}
{% for key, stream in insight.activity.streams.items() %}
- {{ key }}: {{ stream.data | length }} points
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- No streams were stored for this activity.
{% endif %}
